OK, I need to call it a day for now but we're failing to find it in `name_to_node` here:
https://www.github.com/tensorflow/tensorflow/blob/master/tensorflow/core/common_runtime/direct_session.cc#L822
and when using `InteractiveSession` we're not inserting it in the [values](https://www.github.com/tensorflow/tensorflow/blob/master/tensorflow/core/common_runtime/direct_session.cc#L932) (only `add` and `mul` get inserted, not any of the placeholders).
